er-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-west-bank-raid/0000018f-5894-d6a5-a5ff-dab402a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军获得的新材料证实两名以色列人质死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/deaths-of-two-israeli-hostages-confirmed-on-basis-of-new-material-obtained-by-idf/0000018f-5882-d348-a7bf-feabc4250000</link><description>负责检查人质状况的医疗委员会的一名成员表示，迄今为止，委员会已经确认了 30 多名此前被认为是人质的人质死亡：他们&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 14:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/deaths-of-two-israeli-hostages-confirmed-on-basis-of-new-material-obtained-by-idf/0000018f-5882-d348-a7bf-feabc4250000</guid></item><item><title>联合航空将以色列航班停飞期限延长至五月底，以色列航空唯一承运人为美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-extends-suspension-of-israel-flights-leaving-el-al-sole-carrier-to-u-s/0000018f-5845-dfc1-adbf-59f53b3b0000</link><description>该航空公司此前已暂停运营至 5 月 9 日。已通知旅行社，5 月 31 日之前的航班将被取消</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 14:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/united-airlines-extends-suspension-of-israel-flights-leaving-el-al-sole-carrier-to-u-s/0000018f-5845-dfc1-adbf-59f53b3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防巨头IAI无意中透露了其最大的外国客户：印度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</link><description>事实证明，去年印度占以色列航空航天工业公司出口收入的四分之一。以色列公司的年度报告中还披露了阿塞拜疆和摩洛哥的详细信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-defense-giant-iai-unwittingly-reveals-its-largest-foreign-customer/0000018f-583d-d348-a7bf-febdda230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列形状的炸肉排因吞并加沙和约旦河西岸而引发争论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-shaped-schnitzel-sparks-a-squabble-by-annexing-gaza-and-the-west-bank/0000018f-57ff-d922-a5af-77ff69cc0000</link><description>独立日的以色列形状的炸肉排因漠视巴勒斯坦领土而受到批评。该公司加入了将以色列爱国主义纳入营销策略的趋势，10 月 7 日后企业纷纷加大力度</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 13:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-shaped-schnitzel-sparks-a-squabble-by-annexing-gaza-and-the-west-bank/0000018f-57ff-d922-a5af-77ff69cc0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争蒙上阴影，欧洲歌唱大赛以流行音乐和抗议拉开帷幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-kicked-off-with-pop-and-protests-as-the-war-in-gaza-casts-a-shadow/0000018f-57d9-dd02-adbf-77d9c7500000</link><description>表演者在马尔默举行的两场半决赛中的第一场上台。这座瑞典城市的安全戒备森严，预计将有约 10 万名欧洲电视网粉丝以及数万名亲巴勒斯坦抗议者涌入这座城市</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-kicked-off-with-pop-and-protests-as-the-war-in-gaza-casts-a-shadow/0000018f-57d9-dd02-adbf-77d9c7500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人忘记了金融危机是什么感觉——但最糟糕的时刻尚未到来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-forgot-what-its-like-to-have-an-economic-crisis-but-the-worst-is-yet-to-come/0000018f-4e73-d6c3-afdf-4f7307ff0000</link><description>加沙战争和立法者不负责任的行为是否会导致以色列发生重大经济危机？迹象令人震惊</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-forgot-what-its-like-to-have-an-economic-crisis-but-the-worst-is-yet-to-come/0000018f-4e73-d6c3-afdf-4f7307ff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长：我对这场战争的了解大部分来自半岛电视台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-justice-minister-most-of-what-i-know-about-the-war-is-from-al-jazeera/0000018f-5797-d6a5-a5ff-d7b709760000</link><description>据 Israel Hayom 报道，右翼司法政变策划者亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 告诉人质家属，他监视着以色列政府最近关闭的卡塔尔车站</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-justice-minister-most-of-what-i-know-about-the-war-is-from-al-jazeera/0000018f-5797-d6a5-a5ff-d7b709760000</guid></item><item><title>加州大学伯克利分校法学教授因与反以色列学生对抗而展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/uc-berkeley-opens-probe-into-law-professor-over-confrontation-with-anti-israel-student/0000018f-57bd-d348-a7bf-f7bdcb0e0000</link><description>该学生向大学防止骚扰和歧视办公室提出投诉后展开调查。这位法学教授说：“令人不安的是，那个故意扰乱我家晚宴的学生......然后竟然厚颜无耻地提出投诉。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/uc-berkeley-opens-probe-into-law-professor-over-confrontation-with-anti-israel-student/0000018f-57bd-d348-a7bf-f7bdcb0e0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯将错过报告以色列是否在加沙违反国际法的最后期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-miss-deadline-on-reporting-whether-israel-violating-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</link><description>一位美国官员预计延迟不会持续超过几天。然而，另一位人士指出，周五之后的任何拖延都将不可避免地被视为拜登政府“做假账”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-miss-deadline-on-reporting-whether-israel-violating-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和他的帮派更喜欢死去的人质，而不是快乐的左翼分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</link><description>战争已经过去七个月了，将这个以色列邪教成员团结在一起的唯一粘合剂仍然是对任何他们认为是“左派”的事物的深不可测的仇恨</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡上周推动拉法攻势，以色列战时内阁反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理的一些行为暗示了推迟达成协议的不可告人的动机。他的办公室否认了此类指控，但尽管以色列官员评估哈马斯即将同意该提议，但内塔尼亚胡不顾战时内阁的反对，开始准备在拉法采取军事行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的加沙人来说，离开拉法就是从一个地狱走向另一个地狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-gazans-leaving-rafah-is-moving-from-one-hell-to-another/0000018f-5411-d348-a7bf-f6b95e5a0000</link><description>以色列军队最近发动了加沙居民的撤离，他们被迫在汗尤尼斯废墟和没有供水和污水基础设施的沿海地带之间做出选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-gazans-leaving-rafah-is-moving-from-one-hell-to-another/0000018f-5411-d348-a7bf-f6b95e5a0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，美国暂停向以色列运送炸弹，以表达对拉法入侵的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/u-s-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel-to-signal-concerns-over-rafah-invasion-official-says/0000018f-570b-d209-a79f-572be3fa0000</link><description>该官员表示，暂停发货的决定是上周做出的，目前尚未就是否稍后继续发货做出最终决定。以色列发言人表示，以色列政府对这些报告没有任何补充。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/u-s-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel-to-signal-concerns-over-rafah-invasion-official-says/0000018f-570b-d209-a79f-572be3fa0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的联盟看起来很安全，因为就连他的对手也拒绝了哈马斯的停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</link><description>民族团结部长和以色列谈判团队反对加沙恐怖组织的提议，该提议与以色列接受的提议在三个关键方面有所不同，其中包括哈马斯拒绝保证在协议第一阶段释放人质。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</guid></item></channel></rss>